## Affiliated Members of Congress

As of January 2025, the [Republican Main Street Partnership](/Republican_Main_Street_Partnership) maintains a list of affiliated members across both chambers of the [United States Congress](/United_States_Congress). This roster, constantly in flux due to elections, retirements, and shifting political allegiances, represents the current legislative footprint of the organization. The numbers themselves are less interesting than the names, each a data point in the ongoing, exhausting saga of political careers.

